Mangaplay Studio — Licensing

This repository bundles two distinct categories of material:

  1. Application code (everything except the fonts/ directory) — MIT.
  2. Bundled font files (fonts/*) — SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1.

Each is covered below. Full per-font licence text ships alongside each font
family at fonts/<family>/LICENCE.txt.


────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Bundled fonts
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The following font families are redistributed under the SIL Open Font
License, Version 1.1 (https://openfontlicense.org). Each family's full
licence text and original copyright notices are preserved in its directory.

  Family              Path                       Copyright
  ──────────────────  ─────────────────────────  ────────────────────────────
  Courier Prime       fonts/courier-prime/       Quote-Unquote Apps
  Courier Prime Sans  fonts/courier-prime-sans/  Quote-Unquote Apps
  Noto Sans           fonts/noto-sans/           The Noto Project Authors
  Noto Sans Mono      fonts/noto-sans-mono/      The Noto Project Authors
  Noto Sans JP        fonts/noto-sans-jp/        The Noto Project Authors
  Noto Sans KR        fonts/noto-sans-kr/        The Noto Project Authors
  Noto Sans SC        fonts/noto-sans-sc/        The Noto Project Authors
  Noto Sans TC        fonts/noto-sans-tc/        The Noto Project Authors
  Noto Sans Thai      fonts/noto-sans-thai/      The Noto Project Authors

The SIL OFL permits use, study, modification, and redistribution of the
fonts (including embedding in software) provided that the licence and
copyright notice are preserved. See each fonts/<family>/LICENCE.txt for
the authoritative terms.


